---
title: Phantom Pork Tenderloin with Apple Eyeballs, Kale, and Beheaded Sweet Potatoes
description: We thought the combination of pork and apples was impossible to beat... until our chefs added sweet potatoes. This autumnal dynamic duo just became a triple threat, and we can’t wait for you to try it.
